arStrings.szText: {c_important}Penetrating Shot{/c} makes enemies hit {c_important}{u}Vulnerable{/u}{/c} for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. Every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} casts of {c_important}Penetrating Shot{/c} will fire an arrow that bounces off walls and scenery and deals {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%x|]{/c} more damage.
